Welcome to BSDBoot Image, the memory based BSD distribution.
------------------------------------------------------------

1) To install MyBee (FreeBSD-based appliance for virtual env (jail/bhyve)), please type:

  fetch https://myb.convectix.com/auto
  sh auto

2) To install ClonOS (FreeBSD-based appliance for virtual env (jail/bhyve) via WEB UI), please type:

  fetch https://clonos.convectix.com/auto
  sh auto

3) To install vanilla FreeBSD 14.0-RELEASE, please type:

  bsdinstall

*** Another possibilites: ***

You can expand and customize this image yourself, gaining new opportunities. 
Other official extensions:

'bsdboot bhyve'  - Fetch & enable bhyve hypervisor module
'bsdboot cbsd'   - Fetch & Enable 'CBSD' module
'bsdboot attach' - Attach network disk
'bsdboot add'    - Add remote CBSDBoot node
